{"tid":202741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"28歲男聲稱遭姐夫企圖雞姦　警暫列非禮調查","createTime":"2017-04-15T17:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T17:51:44.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec31087604ac291ca78fe235f2dea1271824a8f","tid":202741,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"大埔發生男子疑遭非禮案。據悉，事主28歲，他報稱今早7時許，於大埔區一個單位內疑遭其姐夫企圖雞姦。他其後自行前往大埔醫院求診，並通知院內職員報案。警方初步調查後，將案件暫列非禮，交大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫時未有人被捕。消息指，事主疑有情緒問題，為大埔醫院病人，說話語無倫次。"},{"pid":"7fc1136000f7897d269fd2469b2413fb08eb51fb","tid":202741,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0c7a1839498bf8aa9a2ee1da3c7bca8f2a16f6","tid":202741,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:25:09.000Z","msg":"姐目前犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02706f6d8f9a32c5cf328ac85f54e4b019fdbe0","tid":202741,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:25:28.000Z","msg":"好難想像佢家姐知道之後會有乜嘢反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7241221113200b0479397ac54b8876e1c5a30da1","tid":202741,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大埔發生男子疑遭非禮案。據悉，事主28歲，他<span style=\"color: red;\">報稱</span>今早7時許，於大埔區一個單位內疑遭其姐夫企圖雞姦。他其後自行前往大埔醫院求診，並通知院內職員報案。警方初步調查後，將案件暫列非禮，交大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫時未有人被捕。消息指，<span style=\"color: red;\">事主疑有情緒問題，為大埔醫院病人，說話語無倫次。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee7d0d97278cdd0b2141c81dab4d9c656786c6f","tid":202741,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"佢一定好大隻<